# Splunk Token Observability Dashboard (SPL Queries)

## 1. Total Token Consumption Over Time
index=main sourcetype="ollama:tokens"
| timechart sum(total_tokens) by model

## 2. Average Latency vs. Token Count
index=main sourcetype="ollama:tokens"
| stats avg(total_duration_ms) as AvgLatency, avg(total_tokens) as AvgTokens by model

## 3. Estimated Cost Attribution (Example: $0.10 per 1k tokens)
index=main sourcetype="ollama:tokens"
| eval cost = (total_tokens / 1000) * 0.10
| stats sum(cost) as TotalCost by model

## 4. Input vs Output Token Ratio
index=main sourcetype="ollama:tokens"
| stats sum(prompt_tokens) as InputTokens, sum(completion_tokens) as OutputTokens
